metadata.name: Contemplation
metadata.description:
Mixed media artwork. Ai + Painting. 2023

I've started this series titled 'Dzogchen' in 2019 and sicne then I've been completing and releasing these works as 1/1's, most are sold-out & well appreciated  and now it's time for an Edition of Contemplation! 

Besides being a beautiful work of art this token will give an early acess to my Big 1/1 Drop on FND this May (~100 SuperAffordable 1/1 artworks)
